title: To the most Excellent Maiestie of the King, and to the most Honorable the Lords and Peeres of this realme As also, to the Honorable the Lords and others, knights, citizens, barons and burgesses in the Commons House of Parliament, now assembled the most humble petition of the churches of God in England, and of every lively member of the same, whereof the Lord Christ Iesus is the head.
